<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="historicalAndRevision" id="id745e6f2c-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7"><heading class="centered smallCaps"><ref href="/us/pl/105/354">Pub. L. 105–354</ref></heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">This amends <ref href="/us/usc/t36/s2501/2">section 2501(2) of title 36</ref> to reflect a change made by section 413 of the Workforce Investment Act of 1998 (<ref href="/us/pl/105/220">Public Law 105–220</ref>, <date date="1998-08-07">Aug. 7, 1998</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/112/1241">112 Stat. 1241</ref>).</p>
</note>
